# --- gatOS: large/generated artifacts that are NOT committed (OS_PLAN.md D9, T0.1) ---
# gitignore has no trailing comments — keep annotations on their own lines.
# built guest image: base.qcow2, kernel, initrd, manifest, keys
guest/out/
# fetched + trimmed QEMU win-x64 bundle (tools/fetch-qemu.*)
vendor/qemu/
# M1 throwaway de-risking code was deleted at the end of M2 (OS_PLAN.md M1); the rule
# stays so local experiments under spike/ never land in git. NOTES.md is the committed
# record of the spike's learnings that M3/M4/M7/M8 must read.
spike/*
!spike/NOTES.md

node_modules/